offers discounted pricing for Batch API workloads, so large indexing runs are usually cheaper than sending the same requests synchronously.\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/concepts/memory.md:- See the OpenAI Batch API docs and pricing for details:\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/concepts/memory.md:  - [https://platform.openai.com/pricing](https://platform.openai.com/pricing)\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/concepts/model-providers.md:- MiniMax (Anthropic‑compatible): `--auth-choice minimax-api`\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/concepts/model-providers.md:See [/providers/minimax](/providers/minimax) for setup details, model options, and config snippets.\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/concepts/model-providers.md:      model: { primary: \"lmstudio/minimax-m2.5-gs32\" },\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/concepts/model-providers.md:      models: { \"lmstudio/minimax-m2.5-gs32\": { alias: \"Minimax\" } },\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/concepts/model-providers.md:            id: \"minimax-m2.5-gs32\",\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/design/kilo-gateway-integration.md:          { \"id\": \"minimax/minimax-m2.5:free\", \"name\": \"Minimax: Minimax M2.5\" }\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/docs.json:      \"source\": \"/minimax\",\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/docs.json:      \"destination\": \"/providers/minimax\"\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/docs.json:                  \"providers/minimax\",\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs/docs.json:                  \"zh-CN/providers/minimax\",\nC:\\Users\\Zwmar\\AppData\\Roa