{"type":"message","id":"72d9597f","parentId":"e7b058a6","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:33:33.556Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach just told me he has free 6-hour RTX 5000 instances on Paperspace. I should make a note of this in the workspace. Let me update the TOOLS.md or a relevant memory file.","thinkingSignature":"31a4db9d8676a748ccae6e5228ee65c1a49dad46c0b9ec3a8044f32fc2a01cc9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jp37m05jysi1_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","old_string":"## GPU / Compute\n- **NO local GPU** — Windows machine has no GPU\n- Paperspace Gradient: cloud GPU (A5000 30GB), account + API key available\n- API key: `131e4cbc99405a0e3af9710cc1607c`\n- Don't suggest local model setups\n\n**Note:** Zach said no Ollama — sandbox uses stateless compositional architecture instead\n\n**Sandbox:** `~/.openclaw/sandbox/`\n**Autonomous pulse:** Task Scheduler \"SandboxPulse\" — every 30 min, 8am-11pm ET\n**Pulse script:** `sandbox/pulse.ps1`","new_string":"## GPU / Compute\n- **NO local GPU** — Windows machine has no GPU\n- Paperspace Gradient: cloud GPU (A5000 30GB), account + API key available\n- API key: `131e4cbc99405a0e3af9710cc1607c`\n- Don't suggest local model setups\n\n**Note:** Zach said no Ollama — sandbox uses stateless compositional architecture instead\n\n**Paperspace RTX 5000 Free Instances:**\n- Zach has free 6-hour RTX 5000 notebook instances on Paperspace\n- Can spin up on demand, up to 6 hours of GPU time per session\n- RTX 5000 = 16GB GDDR6 — fits 2-3 parallel 7B Q4_K_M instances, or 1-2 of 14B Q4_K_M\n- Use for: running local LLM for Breakaway, modal-style burst compute, any GPU task\n\n**Sandbox:** `~/.openclaw/sandbox/`\n**Autonomous pulse:** Task Scheduler \"SandboxPulse\" — every 30 min, 8am-11pm ET\n**Pulse script:** `sandbox/pulse.ps1`"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":